message:
Amazing work being done in San Bernardino County, Ca. 
"A 17-year-old girl was rescued, and a Sacramento man arrested, in a human-trafficking case in San Bernardino, sheriff’s officials said on Tuesday."

data.description: Authorities provided the girl with services and released her into the custody of Children and Family Services to be returned to her family, officials said.
data.title: Investigators rescue human-trafficking victim, 17, in San Bernardino and arrest Sacramento man, authorities say
